"                ພວກເຮົາຈະຕິດຕໍ່ກັບຫາທ່ານໃນໄວໆນີ້.\n"
"\n"
"                <div t-if=\"'website_url' in object.job_id and "
"object.job_id.website_url\" style=\"padding: 16px 8px 16px 8px;\">\n"
